title: Andriy Hrinchenko
text: Andriy Hrinchenko (; born 23 January 1986) is a <a href="professional">professional</a> <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who played for <a href="FC%20Volyn%20Lutsk">FC Volyn Lutsk</a> in the <a href="Ukrainian%20Premier%20League">Ukrainian Premier League</a>.
